<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Twitter</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css"
    integrity="sha512-iBBXm8fW90+nuLcSKlbmrPcLa0OT92xO1BIsZ+ywDWZCvqsWgccV3gFoRBv0z+8dLJgyAHIhR35VZc2oM/gI1w=="
    crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <!-- <script src="script.js" defer ></script> -->
</head>

<body>
  <input type="text" value="<%=token%>" id="token">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sidebar">
      <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>

      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new active">
          <span class="material-icons"> home </span><span class="option"> Home</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new">
          <span class="material-icons"> tag</span><span class="option">Explore</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new">
          <span class="material-icons"> notifications</span><span class="option">Notifications</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new">
          <span class="material-icons"> mail</span><span class="option">Messages</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new">
          <span class="material-icons"> bookmark</span><span class="option">Bookmarks</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new">
          <span class="material-icons"> fact_check</span><span class="option">Lists</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new">
          <span class="material-icons"> person </span><span class="option">Profile</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebarOption">
        <span class="new">
          <span class="material-icons"> more_horiz</span><span class="option">More</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="tweetBtn">Tweet</div>
    </div>
    <div class="home enable">
      <h3>Home</h3>
      <hr />
      <br />
      <div class="tweetBox">
        <a href=""><img src="/assets/images/profile.png" class="user_pfp" /></a>
        <textarea style="
              width: 50%;
              margin-left: 1%;
              resize: none;
              border: none;
              height: 50px;
            " placeholder="What's happening?" maxlength="140"></textarea>
        <button id="tweet_btn">Tweet</button>
      </div>
      <hr />
      <br />
      <div class="content">
        <div>
          <a href=""><img src="https://cdn.trendhunterstatic.com/phpthumbnails/458/458145/458145_1_800.jpeg"
              class="user_pfp" /></a>
        </div>

        <div class="innerContent">

          <div class="username">
            <p><b>Irshad </b> <span id="username">@irshadchauhan</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="usertweet">So whatâ€™s the next big crypto project man ? </div>
          <div class="usericon">
            <span class="material-icons">
              chat_bubble_outline
            </span>
            <span class="material-icons">
              swap_vert
            </span>
            <span class="material-icons">
              favorite_border
            </span>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <div>
          <a href=""><img src="https://cdn.trendhunterstatic.com/phpthumbnails/458/458145/458145_1_800.jpeg"
              class="user_pfp" /></a>
        </div>

        <div class="innerContent">

          <div class="username">
            <p><b>Irshad </b> <span id="username">@irshadchauhan</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="usertweet"> An absolute genius who must be protected at all costs. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
            consectetur adipisicing elit. Labore laborum et commodi voluptatem maiores facere omnis voluptatum
            doloremque. Vero aperiam aut eaque earum sunt explicabo impedit esse alias repudiandae.</div>
          <div class="usericon">
            <span class="material-icons">
              chat_bubble_outline
            </span>
            <span class="material-icons">
              swap_vert
            </span>
            <span class="material-icons">
              favorite_border
            </span>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="userprofile disable">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="headericon">
          <span class="material-icons">
            arrow_back
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="headertext">
          <div>
            <b>Irshad</b>
          </div>
          <div>43 Tweets</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="userbackground">
        <img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1315714997499109376/1618323881/1500x500" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="userprofileimage">
        <div class="userimage">
          <img src="/assets/images/profile.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="editbtn">
          <input type="button" value="Edit profile">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="userbio">
        <div class="personalname"><b>Irshad</b></div>
        <div class="personalusername">@Irshad_Chauhan</div>
        <div class="personalbio">Web Developer</div>
        <div class="personalinfo">
          <div class="personallocation"><span class="material-icons">
              location_on
            </span> Rajkot, India</div>
          <div class="personaldateofbirth"> <span class="material-icons">
              child_care
            </span> Born February 1, 2000 </div>
          <div class="personaldateofjoin">
            <span class="material-icons">
              calendar_month
            </span> Joined october 2020
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="personalnumber">
          <div class="following"> 85 Following</div>
          <div class="followers"> 50 Followers</div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="right-sidebar">
      <input type="search" class="searchtext" placeholder="       Search Twitter" />
      <div class="news">
        <h2>What's Happening</h2>
        <div class="card">
          <a href="https://twitter.com/i/events/1483255084750282753">
            <h4>Ukraine Live News</h4>
          </a>
          <img class="war"
            src="https://c.ndtvimg.com/2022-02/tvpkfh_russia-ukraine-crisis-afp-650_625x300_27_February_22.jpg"
            alt="" />
          <br />
          <p>
            Latest satellite images show deployment of new Russian troops less
            than 50 miles from Ukraine's capital. Russian President Vladimir
            Putin ......
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>